data.text:
Real Madrid's Brazilian-origin football player Vinicius JR was subjected to racist chants by the Valencia fans during the most recent match between the two Spanish clubs. The young player could not hold back his tears in the face of the horrendous racist attack of the hooligans.

Footage shows the hilarious moment Argentine superstar Lionel Messi met his life-size statue that is set to be placed at the South American Football Confederation (CONMEBOL) museum next to the statues of late football greats Diego Armando Maradona and Pele.

A historic event took place at the Premier League as English professional football club, Chelsea, hosted a collective iftar program at the Stamford Bridge Stadium in London. This event was part of the "Open Iftar" events, which have become a tradition in the country through the "Ramadan Tent Project".

Footage shows the frenzy that ensued in the trendy Buenos Aires neighborhood of Palermo on Monday night when hundreds of football fans rushed to a steakhouse after learning that Lionel Messi was dining inside. The restaurant was quickly mobbed by excited supporters, while fans on a street corner could be heard chanting the superstar's name.

NBA spectators enjoyed a mesmerizing Turkish folk dance performance Sunday ahead of the Cleveland Cavaliers vs. LA Clippers game in the U.S. state of Ohio. The Turkish folk dance team from the Turkish State Opera and Ballet performed a three-minute show on the court to promote Turkish culture on the NBA's global stage, which was jointly organized by Türkiye's Yunus Emre Institute (YEE) and the Cleveland Cavaliers.

Drone footage shows thousands of Argentines taking to the streets to celebrate their nation’s third World Cup victory Sunday after Argentina beat France 4-2 in a penalty shootout in Qatar. Following the final whistle, the capital Buenos Aires was filled with jubilant fans of all ages donning the national team's jersey, carrying flags, wearing face paint and banging drums loudly as they descended on the city center, bringing traffic to a standstill. Fans came from across different neighborhoods to line the area around the city's iconic Obelisk -- a traditional spot where the nation’s football fans gather to mark their team's sporting success.

Argentine passengers erupted in cheers on during a Madrid-bound flight from the capital Buenos Aires after the pilot announced: “Your captain is speaking. I am happy to announce that Argentina has won the World Cup.”

Burak Özçivit, who plays the lead role of Osman Gazi, the titular character of the fearless warrior and the founder of the Ottoman Empire, in the Turkish TV drama “The Ottoman”, was welcomed with cheers by his fans in Qatar, where he was in attendance for the World Cup final. The famous actor was able to make his way out of the venue with the help of his bodyguards.

Footage shows Japan fans in Tokyo as they mourn their national football team’s loss to Croatia at the World Cup on Monday. Croatia beat Japan 3-1 (1-1) on penalties Monday to reach the quarterfinals of the 2022 FIFA World Cup.

A Saudi fan reacted to an Israeli correspondent by saying "there is only Palestine, there is no Israel. You're not welcome here", after the match between Saudi Arabia and Poland at the 2022 World Cup in Qatar.
